   CINCINNATI -- Comair Holdings Inc. said 160,232 passengers
boarded its Comair Inc. regional airline during May, 20% more
than a year earlier.
   Revenue passenger miles climbed 30% to 32.9 million, the
company said. A revenue passenger mile is a paying passenger
transported one mile.
