   Who's News:
   Lone Star Technologies
</HL>
<DATE>
06/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS LSST
</CO>
<LP>
   LONE STAR TECHNOLOGIES Inc. (Dallas) -- David E. Blackwell
was named to the new position of chief operating officer of
the company's Lone Star Steel Co. unit. Mr. Blackwell, 51
years old, previously was president and chief executive
officer of Rouge Steel Co., Dearborn, Mich. Mr. Blackwell
also was named vice chairman of the steel unit's board,
increasing board membership to eight. Lone Star is an
oil-field and financial services company.
