Acceptance Corp.: 8.125% 21 to 44 days; 8.10% 45 to 59 days;
8.075% 60 to 89 days; 8.05% 90 to 119 days; 8% 120 to 149
days; 7.95% 150 to 179 days; 7.875% 180 to 270 days.
                                                                                                       

