<HL>
   Business Brief -- Maxwell Communication Corp.:
   Macmillan Unit Buys 51%
   Of Israeli Publisher Keter
</HL>
<DATE>
06/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
